  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou, Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Στάτειος\n                    Εὐτύχης\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Στάτειος\"><span data-text=\"Στάτειος\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Στάτιος\">Στάτειος</span></span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐτύχης\"><span data-text=\"Εὐτύχης\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Εὐτύχης\">Εὐτύχης</span></span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησε</span>  <span data-text=\"ἀμέμ\n                    πτως\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἄμεμπτος\">ἀμέμ-<br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>πτως</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span> · <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\"><span data-text=\"ιϛ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"εἰμί\">ιϛ</span>´</span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"μῆνες\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">μῆνες</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)</span>  <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\"><span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"γ\">γ</span>´</span>  <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ἡμέρας</span> · <span data-text=\"ζ\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"ζ\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ζ</span></span>´ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Στάτειος\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Στάτιος\">Στάτειος</span>  <span data-text=\"Εὐτύχης\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Εὐτύχης\">Εὐτύχης</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔζησε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησε</span>  <span data-text=\"ἀμέμπτως\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἄμεμπτος\">ἀμέμπτως</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"ιϛ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"εἰμί\">ιϛ</span>  <span data-text=\"μῆνες\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">μῆνες</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)</span>  <span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"γ\">γ</span>  <span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ἡμέρας</span>  <span data-text=\"ζ\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">ζ</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou, Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Στάτειος\n                    Εὐτύχης\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Στάτειος\"><span data-text=\"Στάτειος\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Στάτιος\">ΣΤΑΤΕΙΟΣ</span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐτύχης\"><span data-text=\"Εὐτύχης\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Εὐτύχης\">ΕΥΤΥΧΗΣ</span></span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἀμέμ\n                    πτως\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἄμεμπτος\">ΑΜΕΜ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΠΤΩΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span>·<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\"><span data-text=\"ιϛ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"εἰμί\">ΙϚ</span></span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"μῆνες\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΕΣ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\"><span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"γ\">Γ</span></span><br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΑΣ</span>·<span data-text=\"ζ\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"ζ\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ζ</span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Στάτειος\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Στάτιος\">ΣΤΑΤΕΙΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"Εὐτύχης\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Εὐτύχης\">ΕΥΤΥΧΗΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἀμέμπτως\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἄμεμπτος\">ΑΜΕΜΠΤΩΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ιϛ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"εἰμί\">ΙϚ</span><span data-text=\"μῆνες\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΕΣ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"γ\">Γ</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"ζ\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">Ζ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001264_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro 2018-01-08\" src=\"ISic001264_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001264.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro 2018-01-08\" src=\"ISic001264-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001264_copy2_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro 2018-01-08\" src=\"ISic001264_copy2_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001264_copy2.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo Liceo Lazzaro 2018-01-08\" src=\"ISic001264_copy2-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text from photograph</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou</a></p>  <p>Stateios Eutyches, lived blamelessly for 16 years, 3 months, 7 days.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>It is unclear why Kaibel states that Torremuzza's edition (1784) is derivative from Ferrara (1829).</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li>  <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">439</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1784 cl.14 no.140 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</a>  </li><li> Ferrara 1829 390 no.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005</a>  </li><li> Franz 1853 5649b <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a>  </li><li> Rizzo 1904 113 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003144\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003144</a>  </li><li> Libertini 1930 318 no.7 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001871\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001871</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 241 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li><li> Muscolino 2011-2012 227 G10 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Simply cut letters without serifs. Quadrate epsilon, lunate quadrate sigma, rhomboid omega, mu with very short middle strokes. Use of stigma in numerals, and interpuncts to separate numerals.</p> Line 1-6  15-20  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
